Instrument Number: 20211015000987 Document:L Rec: $204.50 Page-1 of 2
Record Date:10/15/2021 2:21 PM
Electronically Recorded King County, WA
AFTER RECORDING RETURN TO:
PERYEA SILVER TAYLOR
901 Fifth Avenue, Suite 820
Seattle, WA 98164-1005
NOTICE OF CLAIM OF LIEN
Grantors / Debtors:
Liu, Siyuan
Grantee / Claimant:
Citiscape Owners Association
Legal Description (abbreviated):
Unit 111, Citiscape Condominium, a Condo
Assessor's Tax Parcel ID #:
Unofficial Copy
1594300110
None
Citiscape Owners Association ("Citiscape") is a Washington corporation created to exercise
the powers and authority of the Association set out in the Declaration recorded in the records of King
County, Washington, at King County Recording No. 9006261216 ("the Declaration"). Section 19.1 of
the Declaration creates a lien against a Lot upon non-payment of an assessment. The lien secures
payment of the unpaid assessment(s) and of all costs and expenses (including reasonable attorneys'
fees) associated with the non-payment. All third parties are put on notice that Citiscape claims a lien
for unpaid assessment(s) dating from February 1, 2021, and for all costs and expenses (including
reasonable attorney's fees) associated with non-payment of the assessment(s), against the property
Reference Nos. of Documents Released or Assigned:
legally described as:
UNIT 111, CITISCAPE CONDOMINIUM, A CONDOMINIUM, ACCORDING TO THE
DECLARATION RECORDED UNDER RECORDING NO. 9006261216, AND ANY
AMENDMENTS THERETO, AND SURVEY MAP AND PLANS IN VOLUME 97 OF
CONDOMINIUMS PLATS, ON PAGES 44 THROUGH 50, INCLUSIVE, AND ANY
AMENDMENTS THERETO, RECORDS OF KING COUNTY, WASHINGTON. SITUATE IN
THE COUNTY OF KING, STATE OF WASHINGTON.
As of October 14, 2021, the total amount owing and secured by the lien was $4,825.36. The
total amount will increase by assessment(s), costs, and expenses that accrue after October 14, 2021,
and prior to foreclosure, including any unposted or unbilled attorney's fees. The total amount
secured by the lien may be a personal obligation of Liu, Siyuan.
